            <h1 style="margin-top: 20px;">School Performance Report: Spark
                Olympiad</h1>
            <p>Dear School Leader,</p>

            <p>We are pleased to share the results for Spark Olympiad 2025
                conducted by EDSSO in collaboration with Prometric.</p>

            <h2>1. Subject Performance & Analysis</h2>
            <p>This section compares the school score against the school and
                overall test averages.</p>

