                    <p><strong>FOCUSED IMPROVEMENT OPPORTUNITY:</strong></p>
                    <p>Current performance trends indicate scope to strengthen
                        alignment with national benchmarks. Additional emphasis
                        on application-level understanding within the
                        EVS/Science curriculum can further support student
                        progress and confidence.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

