                    <h3>Performance Overview - Grade 6</h3>
                    <p><strong>This section compares the school score against
                            the school and overall test averages.</strong></p>
                    <p>The radar chart shows the school's performance across
                        four key subject areas compared to the national test
                        average. Areas where the blue line (School Average)
                        falls inside the red line (Test Average) indicate
                        opportunities for improvement.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>EVS/Science:</strong> School Average 41.67%
                            vs Test Average 55.33%</li>
                        <li><strong>India Awareness:</strong> School Average
                            36.67% vs Test Average 44.52%</li>
                        <li><strong>Math:</strong> School Average 34.89% vs Test
                            Average 42.99%</li>
                        <li><strong>Reading:</strong> School Average 41.86% vs
                            Test Average 53.17%</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <canvas id="performanceChart"></canvas>

