                            <td>6.C-1.4</td>
                            <td>Explores and understands sets of numbers, such
                                as
                                whole numbers, fractions, integers, rational
                                numbers, and real numbers, and their properties,
                                and
                                visualises them on the number line.</td>
                            <td>24.19%</td>
                            <td>42.70%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-1.5</td>
                            <td>Explores the idea of percentage and applies it
                                to
                                solve problems.</td>
                            <td>34.41%</td>
                            <td>41.08%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-2.3</td>
