                            <td>22.58%</td>
                            <td>32.54%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-2.4</td>
                            <td>Poses and solves linear equations to find the
                                value
