                            <td>41.94%</td>
                            <td>58.38%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-3.3</td>
                            <td>Identifies attributes of three-dimensional
                                shapes
                                (cubes, parallelepipeds, cylinders, cones),
                                works
                                hands-on with material to construct these
