                                three-dimensional objects to visualise and solve
                                problem</td>
                            <td>24.19%</td>
                            <td>38.92%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-3.5</td>
                            <td>Understands congruence and similarity as it
                                applies
                                to geometric shapes and identifies similar and
                                congruent triangles.</td>
                            <td>30.32%</td>
                            <td>39.68%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-4.1</td>
                            <td>Discovers, understands, and uses formulae to
