                            <td>38.17%</td>
                            <td>41.35%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-4.2</td>
                            <td>Learns the Baudhayana-Pythagoras theorem on the
