                            <td>14.52%</td>
                            <td>23.24%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-4.3</td>
                            <td>Constructs various designs (using tiling) on a
                                plane
                                surface using different 2D shapes and
                                appreciates
                                their appearances in art in India and around the
                                world.</td>
                            <td>29.03%</td>
                            <td>29.73%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-4.4</td>
                            <td>Develops familiarity with the notion of fractals
                                and
                                identifies and appreciates the appearances of
                                fractals in nature and art in India and around
                                the
                                world.</td>
                            <td>29.03%</td>
                            <td>28.11%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-5.1</td>
                            <td>Collects, organises, and interprets the data
                                using
                                measures of central tendencies such as
                                average/mean,
                                mode, and median.</td>
                            <td>20.56%</td>
                            <td>31.22%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-5.2</td>
                            <td>Selects, creates, and uses appropriate graphical
