                                possibly different, solutions.</td>
                            <td>69.35%</td>
                            <td>72.97%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-8.1</td>
                            <td>Approaches problems using programmatic thinking
