                            <td>43.55%</td>
                            <td>52.61%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-8.2</td>
                            <td>Learns systematic counting and listing,
                                systematic
                                reasoning about counts and iterative patterns,
                                and
                                multiple data representations; learns to devise
                                and
                                follow algorithms, with an eye towards
                                understanding
                                correctness, effectiveness, and efficiency of
                                al</td>
                            <td>42.74%</td>
                            <td>48.65%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td>Math</td>
                            <td>6.C-9.1</td>
                            <td>Recognises how concepts (like counting numbers,
